{"tid":1840332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對於全民防疫，有兩項建議","createTime":"2020-01-24T19:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T19:28:55.000Z","uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb4e87fa05acf871b6af1bef96fb1f6e6d299b6","tid":1840332,"uid":269622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:25:31.000Z","msg":"一，醫護罷工<br />\n就算罷唔到一整日<br />\n罷10分鐘又好，一個鐘又好，按章工作又好<br />\n都一定要有個強硬態度施壓<br />\n逼政府同你地講數<br />\n<br />\n二，全民把關<br />\n其實病人好多仲係跟本就係武漢返來<br />\n想佢冇事就幾難，仲要唔一定發燒<br />\n跟本香港咁多關口仲係無掩雞籠<br />\n就好大問題<br />\n大家要有612既決心<br />\n其實仲急撚過逃犯條例<br />\n真係死人啦<br />\n行動又好支持醫護行動又好<br />\n一定要有人<br />\n真係四通八達到呢<br />\n14個管制站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/contactus/control_points.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fcontactus%2Fcontrol_points.html&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZTx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=9e650855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/contactus/control_points.html</a>"},{"pid":"e4914ade422b536746694994d100cdc912a00949","tid":1840332,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:27:26.000Z","msg":"[封殺高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵大行動 !  香港封關 ! 置頂 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1838537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1838537</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3024c544f0e3635aa4370d1aaad8bb62a1e467f9","tid":1840332,"uid":278355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:28:55.000Z","msg":"p牌想幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}